      "layout": "The page uses a mixed layout approach, blending full-bleed sections with constrained content. The hero prominently features a full-bleed dark background ('Midnight Indigo') with a large, centered product image and left-aligned headline/CTA. Subsequent sections alternate between full-bleed white backgrounds for product listings (often displaying items in a clean, centered grid of 4) and some potentially full-bleed sections with strong, singular background colors like the red observed. Content is generally centered within a comfortable maximum width when not full-bleed. Vertical rhythm is maintained by consistent spacing between sections (around 48px), creating a spacious and unhurried browsing experience. The navigation is a minimalist sticky top bar, providing persistent access without visual clutter.",
